==English==
===Etymology===
Probably reminiscent of a time when both pots and kettles were made from black [[cast]] [[iron]].

===Idiom===
'''[[pot]] [[calling]] the [[kettle]] [[black]]'''
#{{idiom}} A situation in which somebody comments on or accuses someone else of a [[trait]] which they share.  
#:''I think it's a case of the '''pot calling the kettle black''' when she says he is obsessive.''